ocl:
context MaintenanceTicket
inv: self.openedAt <> null and self.status <> null

context AccessPolicy
inv: self.roles->size() >= 1 and self.roles->size() <= 3

context AccessPolicy
inv: self.description.size() >= 10 implies self.description.substring(1, 10) = 'value'

context DataStream
inv: not(self.streamId <> null and self.topic <> null)

context Firmware
inv: self.version <> null implies self.checksum <> null

context IoTPlatform
inv: (self.name <> null and self.version <> null) or (self.name = null and self.version = null)

context Network
inv: self.links->notEmpty() implies self.links->sortedBy(x | x.linkId)->first().linkId <= self.links->sortedBy(x | x.linkId)->last().linkId

context Device
inv: self.tickets->notEmpty() implies self.tickets->sortedBy(x | x.ticketId)->first().ticketId <= self.tickets->sortedBy(x | x.ticketId)->last().ticketId

context Firmware
inv: self.devices->size() >= 4 implies self.devices->asSequence()->at(4).deviceId <> null

context Location
inv: self.site <> '' and self.site.size() > 0

context Network
inv: self.links->notEmpty() implies self.links->sortedBy(x | x.bandwidthKbps)->first().bandwidthKbps <= self.links->sortedBy(x | x.bandwidthKbps)->last().bandwidthKbps

context Device
inv: self.dataStreams->forAll(x, y | x <> y implies x.topic <> y.topic)

context IoTPlatform
inv: self.networks->notEmpty() implies self.networks->last().networkId <> null

context APIKey
inv: self.value <> '' and self.value.size() > 0

context Role
inv: self.policies->notEmpty() implies self.policies->sortedBy(x | x.rulesJson)->first().rulesJson <= self.policies->sortedBy(x | x.rulesJson)->last().rulesJson

context AccessPolicy
inv: self.roles->notEmpty() implies self.roles->sortedBy(x | x.roleName)->first().roleName <= self.roles->sortedBy(x | x.roleName)->last().roleName

context AccessPolicy
inv: self.description <> null implies self.policyId <> null

context AccessPolicy
inv: self.rulesJson <> null and self.description <> null

context Network
inv: not(self.name <> null and self.networkId <> null)

context Firmware
inv: (self.devices->size() >= 1 and self.devices->size() <= 1) and (self.devices->size() < 1)

context AccessPolicy
inv: (self.roles->notEmpty() implies self.roles->sortedBy(x | x.roleName)->first().roleName <= self.roles->sortedBy(x | x.roleName)->last().roleName) and (self.roles->isEmpty())

context DataStream
inv: (self.alertRules->notEmpty() implies self.alertRules->sortedBy(x | x.condition)->first().condition <= self.alertRules->sortedBy(x | x.condition)->last().condition) and (self.alertRules->isEmpty())

context AccessPolicy
inv: not(self.description <> '' and self.description.size() > 0)

context AccessPolicy
inv: (self.roles->notEmpty() implies self.roles->last().roleName <> null) and (self.roles->isEmpty())

context User
inv: not(self.roles->forAll(x, y | x <> y implies x.roleName <> y.roleName))
